This package use a loosely based version of this code recipe from developer.force.com, by LukeJFreeland :
(http://developer.force.com/cookbook/recipe/automated-unit-test-execution)

and a modified version of Apex Tooling API wrapper, REST version, from Andrew Fawcett & James Loghry
(https://github.com/afawcett/apex-toolingapi)

Thanks to them !